features: The Baby Einstein Curious Car Zen Oball Toy Car & Rattle is a flexible, light up toy car that rewards baby’s exploration with lights, rattle beads, and an engaging, flexible texture.
Lightweight, bendable frame is easy for baby to grip and shake and encourages fine motor skill development.
As baby rolls or shakes the car, the center dome lights up to reward baby and support cause and effect learning. Colorful rattle beads engage the senses.
Features Zen the Zebra from Baby Einstein books and shows. Perfect for tummy time, seated play, or fun on-the-go. Compact size lets the toy fit in most diaper bags.
Dimensions 3.5 x 3.5 x 4.5 inches. Wipes clean. Intended for infants ages 3+ months.
body.description: Drive baby’s sensory discovery with the Baby Einstein Curious Car Zen Oball Toy Car & Rattle. This light up toy car features dancing lights and a flexible frame to let baby easily grip and roll this colorful toy. Featuring Zen the Zebra from Baby Einstein shows and books, baby can discover new sights, sounds, or engage in pretend play as they roll Zen to new discoveries! As baby pushes the car, the dome’s colorful lights illuminate to reward baby and promote cause and effect discovery. A bendable frame helps support fine motor skill development as infants ages 3 months and up grasp and shake the toy. Perfect for tummy time, seated play, or on-the-go discovery, this lightweight toy makes a great gift for an infant boy or girl. Wipes clean. Dimensions: 3.5 x 3.5 x 4.5 inches.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Committed to Curiosity Curiosity fuels discovery. It’s the driving force behind painting a portrait or building block towers as high as they can go. It propels us to run our fingers along the bark of a tree or strum a guitar to create a song. From toys to infant gear, to books to media, Baby Einstein meets children where they are, and inspires them to use curiosity to discover their place in the world. We celebrate each child’s unique gifts and individual development timelines and strive to support parents in their role as “Baby’s First Teacher.”

Our Learning Philosophy We believe that play should be comprised of Open-Ended Experiences. That Real-World Discovery introduces great lessons and inspires curiosity. We believe that learning should be experiential, rewarding, and drive Confidence Development. That Multi-Sensorial Engagement helps us interpret and understand the world, and that Creative Thinking Stimulation supports mental agility. These principles make up what we call the Einstein Way and inspire our pursuit of creating products and content that prepare children for their future.

Inspired by Einstein, Intended for Little Minds, Supported by Science Baby Einstein is known for quality products that inspire exploration, boost confidence, and grow with children’s interests and abilities. Our toys and gear are intuitive, easy to use, and built with baby in mind so they’re encouraged to develop and thrive at their own pace. Montessori-inspired design and content rooted in STEAM provide a “whole child” approach that keep children (and parents!) playful and curious.

Education + Entertainment = Edutainment We create intentional and inclusive media with a focus on interactivity and real-world discovery. Baby Einstein “edutainment” makes new concepts fun and attainable for small children. Our inquisitive, loveable animal characters introduce educational content like numbers, counting, first words, colors, manners, and world cultures in concrete, accessible formats through song and short, age-appropriate video programming.
